  "text": "Jiří is probably the best recruiter I know and now he's up for grabs!\n\nWith his affinity to communities, Python, and junior devs, we had some great time building the Python community together, and helping juniors to prepare for their first job. I'm very happy Jiří accepted my invitations to give talks and trainings, and to share advice in the Junior Guru podcast.\n\nIf Red Hat goes through layoffs, that's definitely some sad news. Your company can now hire Jiří though, and that's some good news!",
